}

#message:1A:127
{
[Style Tattle]
[EnableCDownNext]
That's Donlon, the Shaman.[BR]
[Pause 15]...Or at least,[Pause 5] it's a[BR]
holograph of him anyway.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
What's he doing out here?[BR]
[Pause 10]You know, Mario,[Pause 5] if he can[BR]
make my life better, you[BR]
better take the chance.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
I can't just [Shake]abra-kadabra[/fx][BR]
babes into my lap.[BR]
[Pause 10]That'd be too convenient...[Wait][End]
}

#message:1A:128
{
[Style Tattle]
[EnableCDownNext]
That's PeguinoGod43, and he[BR]
draws erotic art.[BR]
[Pause 15]If you want to know his real[BR]
name, you'll have to ask him.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
What a hobby though![BR]
[Pause 5]Must be nice getting boobs[BR]
to look at for free. I envy.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
I mean that's cool and all, but[BR]
I prefer the real thing.[BR]
[Pause 5]We gotta get back to hunting[BR]
down those babes, Mario.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
Pop a squat and get looking.[Pause 10][BR]
I won't sit by and age a[BR]
hundred years while you goof[BR]
off and meander.[Wait][End]
}

#message:1A:129
{
