#message:1A:12A
{
[Style Tattle]
[EnableCDownNext]
This is Tyrant, the Broozer.[BR]
He's one of Lady Bow's servants.[BR]
[Pause 10]Poor guy. Almost feel bad for him.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
Then again, he did beat the crud[BR]
out of us, so... [Pause 3]karma![BR]
[Wait][Next]
He's just like the rest of us,[BR]
ready to be at her service when[BR]
she needs us most.[BR]
[Wait][next]
[PrintRising]"[SaveColor][Color:00]At your service, my queen![RestoreColor]"[/fx][BR]
[Pause 5]Or something like that.[Wait][End]
}

#message:1A:12B
{
[Style Tattle]
[EnableCDownNext]He's the archaeologist, Kolorado.[BR]
[Pause 10]Full name Charles Kolorado.[BR]
[Pause 10]What's he doing here in the port[BR]
of [SaveColor][Color:05]Kinoko Town[RestoreColor], hmm?[BR]
[Wait][Next]
Ah you know what, I think I[BR]
get it.[BR]
[Pause 10]His wife's mad at him and[BR]
he's planning a breakaway.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
Happens a lot in relationships[BR]
actually, don't ya know, Mario?[BR]
[Pause 15]Sometimes when Goomama raises[BR]
her voice at Goompapa...[BR]
[Wait][Next]
He hides in a tree for a few hours[BR]
until she goes for a nap.[BR]
[Pause 12]Dang, I guess even he's afraid[BR]
of her...[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

#message:1A:12C
{
