#message:1A:130
{
[Style Tattle]
[EnableCDownNext]He's the archaeologist, Kolorado.[BR]
[Pause 10]Full name Charles Kolorado.[BR]
[Pause 10]This guy is even more tenacious[BR]
than me, I swear![BR]
[Wait][Next]
